1
00:00:13,279 --> 00:00:15,519
Princess, only you may enter.

2
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:19,800
Wait for me outside.

3
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:20,160
Yes.

4
00:00:26,839 --> 00:00:27,320
Please.

5
00:00:49,159 --> 00:00:50,960
You're this brazen about it,

6
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:53,320
building the Human Body Factory under a hospital?

7
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:55,039
The most dangerous place

8
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:56,880
is the safest place.

9
00:00:57,399 --> 00:01:00,000
What kind of experiments are conducted here?

10
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:02,799
Bacterial implantation in living subjects,

11
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,719
herbal effects on living subjects, that sort of thing.

12
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:08,359
I can only give you a rough idea.

13
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:11,239
But for anti-cancer drugs like yours,

14
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,799
we can reach conclusions in minutes.

15
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,480
So do you

16
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:19,359
use actual cancer patients for the tests?

17
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,879
This is our core laboratory.

18
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:25,760
Only core staff are allowed inside.

19
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:27,400
I'll register your information.

20
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,079
During our partnership,

21
00:01:29,599 --> 00:01:30,840
you'll have access to this place.

22
00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:45,120
Please, come in.

23
00:01:57,599 --> 00:02:00,200
Lab 007, used for human vivisection,

24
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,719
holds plenty of the evidence we need.

25
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,719
I wore these contact lenses of yours

26
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:05,879
and captured a lot of footage.

27
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:16,759
Thanks for your hard work, Senior Sister.

28
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,960
Human experimentation is illegal and unethical.

29
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:22,599
I have to put a stop to it.

30
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,560
Yeah.

31
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:28,960
What are you doing here?

32
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,680
I'm joining tonight's operation.

33
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,000
This isn't a game.

34
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,520
You think I'm playing around?

35
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,719
It's too dangerous.

36
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:42,120
I don't want to drag you into this.

37
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,360
Drag me in?

38
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,199
I'm not doing this for you.

39
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:46,360
I'm a journalist.

40
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,280
Investigating is my job too.

41
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:50,759
You're really going?

42
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:51,960
Yeah.

43
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,479
Ren Feifan, let me go!

44
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,560
Ren Feifan, put me down!

45
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,560
Ren Feifan!

46
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,199
Brother, wait.

47
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:03,199
The door on the right uses facial-retinal recognition.

48
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,080
I've already uploaded your data.

49
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,280
You should be able to open it directly.

50
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,599
Recognition failed.

51
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,680
Recognition failed.

52
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,920
Ren Ran, what's going on?

53
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,360
Cracking password.

54
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,879
The contact lens camera must be causing interference.

55
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,639
Brother, take them off and try again.

56
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:22,959
Okay.

57
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,800
Cracking password.

58
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:33,480
Recognition successful.

59
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:44,000
Hey, who are you?

60
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:45,360
I've never seen you before.

61
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,720
This guy isn't registered.

62
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,199
Which group are you from?

63
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:55,360
Group A02, myocarditis patient.

64
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,759
Subcutaneous light not visible.

65
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,800
Group A02, stop right there.

66
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,959
The handover happens here.

67
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:01,959
You can't go any further.

68
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:04,920
Yes, sir.

69
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:05,920
Come on.

70
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,639
You're new here?

71
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,959
I'm the substitute doctor.

72
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:17,959
Doctor Liu's out today, so he asked me to drop him off.

73
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,040
I'm the substitute doctor.

74
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:21,680
Doctor Liu's out on a call today.

75
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,600
He had me deliver the patient.

76
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,360
I'm done with my work too.

77
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,199
Let's head out together.

78
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:26,600
Hold on.

79
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:29,639
Clock out first.

80
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,079
Let's go.

81
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:46,160
Connection successful.

82
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,839
Brother, you're fine to walk out with them.

83
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,319
I've already hacked into the network.

84
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,560
Data is being transferred.

85
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,120
Got it.

86
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,600
What are you doing here?

87
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,199
Brother Hui, what a coincidence.

88
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:18,399
My brother and I are going to pull off a big job.

89
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:19,399
I'll fill you in later.

90
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,279
Where's your brother?

91
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,879
He's busy. I've gotta go pick him up.

92
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,879
Alright, go on.

93
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,519
I just saw Brother Hui.

94
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,279
Brother Hui?

95
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:54,800
Yeah.

96
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,160
Let me sync up with Dazhuang's frequency.

97
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,279
President Wang.

98
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:14,399
What brings you here?

99
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:25,959
How's the progress lately?

100
00:07:26,639 --> 00:07:27,639
We're speeding things up.

101
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,000
Make sure you hurry.

102
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,600
Yes, sir.

103
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:45,040
This guy...

104
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,199
Why does he look familiar?

105
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:01,720
Useless idiots!

106
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:08,279
These are all imported instruments.

107
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,279
Can you afford to replace them if you break them?

108
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,120
Now get back to work!

109
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,079
President Wang, the experiment next door is about to start.

110
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,279
The radiation levels will be high.

111
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,600
Perhaps you should step away for now.

112
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,000
This is all of it.

113
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,240
Master, did you see it?

114
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:09,120
Yes.

115
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:13,039
This evidence should take down the Wangs for good.

116
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,360
His handwriting's worse than mine.

117
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:26,759
Stay sharp. Don't let your guard down.

118
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,120
Got it.

119
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,240
This is perfect.

120
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,279
I didn't expect to catch Wang Wenhao on camera.

121
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,759
The evidence is rock solid.

122
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,840
Senior Sister really is amazing.

123
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,960
She actually managed to lure Wang Wenhao out.

124
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,600
So it was all part of Master's plan.

125
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:56,120
Alright, the data transfer is complete.

126
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,320
Get ready to pull out.

127
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,559
You got it.

128
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,080
Wait.

129
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,799
Master, how do I get out?

130
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:05,279
The southeast vent leads to the hospital's back door.

131
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,559
We'll wait for you across the street.

132
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:07,159
Okay.

133
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,279
Copy that.

134
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:15,480
We really owe Dazhuang for this one.

135
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,240
He's gonna be showing off for a while now.

136
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,080
It'll be dawn soon.

137
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:20,919
Let's go pick him up at the meeting point.

138
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,759
Then we're heading home.

139
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:22,559
Okay.

140
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,120
You killed Dazhuang.

141
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,080
You took the Human Body Factory files.

142
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:13,159
How long did you think you'd last?

143
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:19,639
You killed Li Xiande too.

144
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,600
Yes.

145
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,559
I admit it.

146
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,000
I definitely have the evidence.

147
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,919
But I thought it over,

148
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,919
and I'll be safer with you as the middleman.

149
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,039
Why is it you?

150
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:49,519
Answer it.

151
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,919
So we're on the same side.

152
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,600
Hello, Ruojin.

153
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:09,879
I'm here.

154
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,279
Where are you?

155
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:16,840
Just as I thought, you're the one Xu Ruojin trusts most.

156
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:20,200
No wonder she'd risk so much to help you.

157
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,000
Listen to me,

158
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:24,600
Xu Ruojin is in my hands right now.

159
00:12:25,799 --> 00:12:28,320
I know that to you and Wang Wenhao,

160
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,559
she's the most important person.

161
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:30,000
Of course,

162
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,960
Director Ren is much more honorable than Wang Wenhao.

163
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:38,320
So let's make a deal.

164
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,840
I'm taking Xu Ruojin with me.

165
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:43,279
As my get-out-of-jail-free card.

166
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,279
Once I've escaped safely,

167
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:47,879
I'll return her and the evidence to you.

168
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,559
Ruojin! Ruojin!

169
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,039
Li Xian...

170
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,159
Take him away.
